---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Karen Arze | Home">
  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 50px;">
    <div style="width: 180px; height: 180px; background: #e1f0ff; border: 5px solid white; border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 20px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); overflow: hidden; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
      <span style="color: #0056b3; font-weight: bold;">Photo</span>
    </div>
    <h1 style="color: #003366; font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 10px;">Karen Arze</h1>
    <p style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; color: #555; line-height: 1.8;">
      Quick to adapt and eager to learn, I am reliable enough to take on leadership roles and always strive for work that can model what I would like to see in others. I'm always enthusiastic to apply my experiences into an environment that appreciates organization and efficiency!
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="background: #f8fbff; border-radius: 15px; padding: 25px; margin-bottom: 40px; border-left: 5px solid #a2c2e1;">
    <h3 style="color: #003366; margin-top: 0;">Personal Information</h3>
    <p style="margin: 5px 0;">📍 <strong>State:</strong> Virginia</p>
    <p style="margin: 5px 0;">📞 <strong>Phone:</strong> 757-515-****</p>
    <p style="margin: 5px 0;">✉️ <strong>Email:</strong> karen**********@yahoo.com</p>
  </div>

  <h2 style="color: #003366; text-align: center;">My Interests</h2>
  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 20px;">
    <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid #eef2f7; padding: 20px; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);">
      <h4 style="color: #0056b3;">🌊 Long Walks</h4>
      <p style="font-size: 0.95rem;">Even if it's a bit of a drive, it's always worth being able to see the beautiful sunrise!</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid #eef2f7; padding: 20px; border-radius: 15px;">
      <h4 style="color: #0056b3;">💃 Dancing</h4>
      <p style="font-size: 0.95rem;">I know Bachata and Meringue; currently practicing Jazz and Salsa. Dancing is when I feel the most like myself!</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid #eef2f7; padding: 20px; border-radius: 15px;">
      <h4 style="color: #0056b3;">🍳 Cooking</h4>
      <p style="font-size: 0.95rem;">I love being experimental! I challenge myself to make something my family will enjoy with whatever ingredients I have.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: #eef2f7; padding: 20px; border-radius: 15px; text-align: center;">
      <h4 style="color: #003366;">❤️ My Children</h4>
      <p style="font-size: 0.95rem;">My Son and Daughter are my pride and joy! They will always be my babies at heart.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
